<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Password Reset OTP | Bighil</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');
    
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #111827;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    .email-wrapper {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ffffff, #f3f4f6);
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .header {
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2563EB, #7C3AED);
    }
    
    .logo {
      width: 120px;
      height: auto;
    }
    
    .content {
      padding: 32px 24px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    
    .title {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #2563EB;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .message {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #4B5563;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    
    .otp-box {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #2563EB, #7C3AED);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    
    .otp-title {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 36px;
      letter-spacing: 8px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #000;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    
    .expiry {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #ffffff;
      opacity: 0.9;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    
    .instructions {
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    
    .instructions-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    
    .security-note {
      background-color: #fff4e5;
      border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    
    .security-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #b45309;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    
    .security-message {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #92400e;
    }
    
    .help {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    
    .help-message {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6B7280;
    }
    
    .help-link {
      color: #2563EB;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .help-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 24px;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    
    .social {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    
    .social-icon {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 8px;
    }
    
    .company-info {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9CA3AF;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    
    .copyright {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9CA3AF;
    }
    
    .highlight {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #2563EB;
    }
    
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #2563EB, #7C3AED);
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 12px;
      }
      
      .otp-code {
        font-size: 28px;
        letter-spacing: 6px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="email-wrapper">

      
      <div class="content">
        <h1 class="title">Reset Your Password</h1>
        
        <p class="message">Hi <%= userName %>,</p>
        
        <p class="message">
          We received a request to reset your password for your Bighil account. 
          To verify it's you, enter the following one-time password (OTP) in the password reset page.
        </p>
        
        <div class="otp-box">
          <p class="otp-title">YOUR ONE-TIME PASSWORD</p>
          <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
          <p class="expiry">Valid for 30 minutes only</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="instructions">
          <h3 class="instructions-title">How to reset your password:</h3>
          <ol style="margin-left: 20px; color: #4B5563;">
            <li>Enter the 6-digit code shown above</li>
            <li>Create a new secure password</li>
            <li>Start using your account with the new password</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
        
        <div class="security-note">
          <h3 class="security-title">Security Tips</h3>
          <p class="security-message">
            • Never share your OTP with anyone, including Bighil staff<br>
            • Use a unique password that you don't use for other accounts<br>
            • Include a mix of letters, numbers, and special characters
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <p class="message">
          If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email or <span class="highlight">contact our support team</span> immediately to secure your account.
        </p>
        
        <div class="help">
          <p class="help-message">
            Need help? Contact our support team at
            <a href="mailto:support@bighil.com" class="help-link">support@bighil.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">

        
        <p class="company-info">
          Bighil Technologies • 123 Business Avenue, Tech City 10001
        </p>
        
        <p class="copyright">
          &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Bighil. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
